urls.description: Book an appointment to get the COVID-19covid 19 vaccine at a go-vaxx mobile vaccine clinic.

data.text:
Hop on the #GOVAXX bus for your 1st or 2nd dose of a #COVID19 vaccine. 

Our mobile vaccine bus will be at the Upper Canada Mall in Newmarket on Saturday, September 11 from 10:00 a.m. to 8:00 p.m.

No appointment needed. https://t.co/MB1MrskW0z https://t.co/5KOCcltn4Y
